=== 鹅 ===
[[File:Domestic_Goose.jpg|thumb]], 野生[[灰雁|灰雁]]的一种后代]]
鹅的野生祖先有两个物种。[[灰雁|灰雁]]至少3000年以前就已经被埃及人驯化<ref name=faogeese>{{cite web |url=http://www.fao.org/DOCREP/005/Y4359E/y4359e03.htm |title=Origins and Breeds of Domestic Geese |author1=Buckland, R. |author2=Guy, G. |publisher=FAO Agriculture Department |accessdate=February 17, 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Zy94TJcf?url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/Y4359E/y4359e03.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大约1000年后，西伯利亚居住的人类将另一种物种[[鸿雁|鸿雁]]驯服，这种被驯服的鹅又称为中国鹅<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bird-friends.com/BirdPage.php?name=White%20Chinese%20Goose |title=White Chinese Goose |author=Streit, Scott |year=2000 |work=Bird Friends Of San Diego County |accessdate=February 17, 2014 |archive-date=2020-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126231556/http://www.bird-friends.com/BirdPage.php?name=White%20Chinese%20Goose |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这两种鹅互相杂交，使得鸿雁家鹅头部的肉瘤在杂交后代产生了不同程度的变化。尽管鹅的驯化时间久，但是并没有取得像鸡鸭同等重要的商业地位<ref name=faogeese/>。

